    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and she\u2019s a total beauty! It\u2019s been super well-loved and maintained, so it\u2019s running great and ready for all your upcoming road trips. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of being enjoyed, but honestly, it still looks fantastic and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, comfy ride that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 33500.0,
