    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This driver-focused example retains its factory individual throttle bodies and delivers linear power through a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a structural subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. The suspension retains its factory geometry with crisp turn-in, and the engine exhibits strong compression and no vacuum leaks. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, making this an ideal candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes performance and mechanical integrity over showroom cosmetics.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
