    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a well-maintained daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, having been regularly waxed; while you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the trunk\u2014typical for a car of this age\u2014the body remains straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with leather upholstery that remains supple and supportive, showing only light entrance wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. It starts perfectly, shifts smoothly through all gears, and the braking is firm and responsive. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, with full service records available for your review. This is a reliable, honest car that has been loved and looked after, ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
